select guruobj_userid as USER_ID from bansecr.GURUOBJ where guruobj_OBJECT in('GPBADMN','GPBADMA')  and GURUOBJ_USERID not like 'BAN_%'
union
select GURUCLS_userid as USER_ID from bansecr.gurucls
where gurucls_class_code in (select GURUOBJ_USERID from bansecr.GURUOBJ where guruobj_OBJECT in('GPBADMN','GPBADMA')  and GURUOBJ_USERID like 'BAN_%')
union
select spriden_id as USER_ID from SPRIDEN where SPRIDEN_CHANGE_IND is null and 
spriden_pidm in (
select gobeacc_pidm from general.gobeacc where 
gobeacc_username in (select guruobj_userid as USER_ID from bansecr.GURUOBJ where guruobj_OBJECT in('GPBADMN','GPBADMA')  
and GURUOBJ_USERID not like 'BAN_%'))
